data.description: Beautiful Home in a great subdivision, well taken care of! Vinyl fence around the back yard gives you privacy and enjoyment for yourself and your family when relaxing in your beautiful brick paved patio. Patio has built in lighting. Close to schools, shopping and transportation. Many updates include Roof & Fence within 5 years, Central Air Condition less than a year. Seller is removing light fixture in daughter's room. Freezer and fridge don't stay.
